Rulings.Cat:
● 'Superancient Deepsea King Coelacanth's' effect that negates card effects when it is targeted is a Quick Effect. This effect can be activated multiple times during the same turn and it can be activated during the Damage Step.
● When 'Exiled Force's' effect targets 'Superancient Deepsea King Coelacanth', 'Exiled Force's' effect can be negated even though it is now in the GY.

PSCT.Edison:
① Once per turn: You can discard 1 card; Special Summon as many Level 4 or lower Fish as possible from your Deck (they can't attack, also negate their effects).
② If this card is targeted by a card effect (Quick): You can Tribute 1 other Fish; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that card.
